.:Plot:.
Show chronicles the horror stories behind people's unfortunate tattoos and their attempts to fix them. The series, will include tattoos ranging from the hilarious to downright disturbing, with reenactments that will show how these people wound up with their ink. The show's contestants will then go under the needle to remove or cover them.
